title: Coeur d'Alene at Lake City or Clearwater Valley (Kooskia) at Lapwai
text:
Coeur d'Alene at Lake City or Clearwater Valley (Kooskia) at Lapwai Polls closed October 14 at 11:00 p.m. Tom will then announce the winning game on live TV. Post to Facebook Coeur d'Alene at Lake City or Clearwater Valley (Kooskia) at Lapwai Polls closed October 14 at 11:00 p.m. Tom will then announce the winning game on live TV.  //on.krem.com/1LmbhmX   Coeur d'Alene at Lake City or Clearwater Valley (Kooskia) at Lapwai Tom Sherry, KREM 12:02 p.m. PDT October 9, 2015 Gear sits on the field (Photo: Denis Poroy, AP) CONNECT TWEET   
Tom's Tailgate Weather is back for another high school football season! 
Each fall, Chief Meteorologist Tom Sherry visits high school football games around the Inland Northwest. But students, parents and football fans must vote on KREM.com to decide where he stops. 
Voting opened October 9 for football fans at the following high schools: Coeur d'Alene at Lake City and Clearwater Valley (Kooskia) at Lapwai.
